Spatial data object of lines defining major Tampa Bay segments

Source: R/tbseglines.R
tbseglines.Rd

Spatial data object of lines defining major Tampa Bay segments

tbseglines

Format

A simple features sf object (LINESTRING) with 3 features and 1 field, +proj=longlat +ellps=WGS84 +datum=WGS84 +no_defs

See also

Other utilities: bsmap, epcdata, fimdata, fimstations, iwrraw, stations, targets, tbniref, tbnispp, tbseg, tbshed, tidalcreeks, tidaltargets

Examples

library(sf)
plot(st_geometry(tbseglines))
